WEBVTT

00:00:01.381 --> 00:00:02.976
Something happened

00:00:04.571 --> 00:00:07.038
while I was studying in the seminary

00:00:07.683 --> 00:00:10.198
and training to be a priest.

00:00:11.703 --> 00:00:15.258
I came in contact
with a different idea of life.

00:00:16.933 --> 00:00:21.528
An idea of life that contradicted
the main teachings of religion --

00:00:21.552 --> 00:00:22.702
humanism.

00:00:24.294 --> 00:00:28.499
Some of you may be wondering,
what on earth is humanism?

00:00:29.945 --> 00:00:32.609
Humanism is a way of thinking and living